  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and coriander seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add toasted buckwheat flour and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add malted milk powder, salt, and water, and stir well.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and serve in a bamboo tray."
